Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.77,0:01:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我是奈美\N是坐电车上下班的OL
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.80,0:01:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,才开始上班\N薪水也不是很多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.91,0:01:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,工作很忙\N跟男朋友见面也很少了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.62,0:01:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,学生时期的我也想过未来\N对于我的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,痴汉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.73,0:02:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,别出声哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.78,0:02:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,别出声哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.83,0:09:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,继续咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.90,0:10:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,别出声哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.84,0:14:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,别出声哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.61,0:14:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了把
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.67,0:17:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,明天再来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.76,0:18:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我害怕到睡不着\N又怕遇到痴汉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.71,0:18:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你摸我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.83,0:19:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.74,0:19:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.71,0:20:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么不叫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.74,0:21:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天很爽把
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你上瘾了哦\N请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.73,0:21:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,一般人第二次是不会再穿短裙的\N你为何穿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,关你什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.72,0:22:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,今天让我爽把
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.70,0:22:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了把
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.71,0:22:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.69,0:22:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.72,0:24:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服把\N哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.70,0:24:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你少来了\N快点
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.71,0:24:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.72,0:25:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我吹
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.70,0:25:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你想让大家认识你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.71,0:25:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.72,0:29:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.70,0:29:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你兴奋了把
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.71,0:29:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N少来了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.73,0:33:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,吸干净
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.91,0:34:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天下车后我跑去厕所\N因为嘴里有精液的残留
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.82,0:34:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是我兴奋了吗\N不 我可是受害者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.72,0:39:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.79,0:40:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.83,0:40:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,期待吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.84,0:40:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,要干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.88,0:40:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.34,0:41:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.78,0:42:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,想继续被侵犯把
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.84,0:42:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,住手\N热热的把
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.71,0:42:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你好色哦
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.62,0:42:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.81,0:43:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,别出声哦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.69,0:45:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,来把
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.84,0:45:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,变硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.93,0:46:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好硬哦
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.84,0:46:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,痒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.30,0:54:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.80,0:55:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.93,1:02:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.87,1:03:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,想要我射出来把
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.48,1:15:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.87,1:16:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.61,1:17:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.65,1:21:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次被巨大的肉棒插入了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.76,1:21:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我没有反抗\N我怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.67,1:21:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我又坐上同一个车厢呢
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.71,1:22:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你很期待把
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.94,1:23:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,对不对\N因为你都不反抗
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.81,1:23:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,反抗也没用
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.78,1:23:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.76,1:23:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你无话可说了把
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.77,1:23:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,说了也没用
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.72,1:23:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,等很久了把
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.79,1:23:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你才是变态
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.80,1:24:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,想摸把\N哪有
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.75,1:24:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.96,1:24:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服把
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.77,1:27:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,来接吻
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.77,1:31:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我吹
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.75,1:31:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.76,1:34:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,想怎么样
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.83,1:34:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,来插我
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.86,1:35:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.83,1:35:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.91,1:35:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.88,1:36:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.65,1:36:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,说啊
Dialogue: 0,1:36:15.63,1:36:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了把
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.93,1:39:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好湿
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.91,1:39:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,想怎么样
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.71,1:39:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,想要把
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.89,1:39:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,来插我
Dialogue: 0,1:51:36.88,1:51:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了把\N没有
Dialogue: 0,1:51:44.96,1:51:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,少来了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:49.73,1:51:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我讨厌你
Dialogue: 0,1:55:41.69,1:55:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了\N天啊
Dialogue: 0,1:55:53.81,1:55:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么射了
Dialogue: 0,1:56:00.78,1:56:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,别闹了
Dialogue: 0,1:56:14.73,1:56:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,还很硬
Dialogue: 0,1:56:19.86,1:56:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,还想要把\N是你想要把
Dialogue: 0,1:57:06.84,1:57:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他是来试探我的\N射了就走了
Dialogue: 0,1:57:24.83,1:57:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,真是不甘心
Dialogue: 0,1:58:30.90,1:58:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次看你星期五搭车
Dialogue: 0,1:58:42.64,1:58:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你是在诱惑我把
Dialogue: 0,1:59:48.71,1:59:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,想要吗
Dialogue: 0,1:59:56.78,1:59:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,到底谁是痴汉呢
Dialogue: 0,2:00:02.65,2:00:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,变大了
Dialogue: 0,2:00:09.63,2:00:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,湿了把
Dialogue: 0,2:03:37.74,2:03:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服把
Dialogue: 0,2:03:41.77,2:03:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,湿了
Dialogue: 0,2:03:46.91,2:03:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天被插入了把
Dialogue: 0,2:08:48.61,2:08:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,变大了
Dialogue: 0,2:11:55.80,2:11:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股翘高
Dialogue: 0,2:12:07.91,2:12:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,想怎么样\N都是插我把
Dialogue: 0,2:12:16.72,2:12:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股翘起来
Dialogue: 0,2:12:24.80,2:12:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,想怎么样
Dialogue: 0,2:12:28.83,2:12:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,想要把
Dialogue: 0,2:12:35.81,2:12:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,想要就说
Dialogue: 0,2:19:27.62,2:19:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你兴奋了把
Dialogue: 0,2:19:33.86,2:19:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服把
Dialogue: 0,2:23:12.61,2:23:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,2:23:26.92,2:23:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,2:23:48.95,2:23:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,吸干净
Dialogue: 0,2:24:35.82,2:24:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我平日就这样好了\N周六我去买新的丝袜把
